REJECTING THE DEPARTMENT OF ADMINISTRATION'S PROPOSED SALARY
INCREASES FOR ELIGIBLE UNCLASSIFIED SERVICE DIRECTORS OF STATE
EXECUTIVE DEPARTMENTS
